Join us for a soulful night of spoken word, food, drinks, and good vibes at @shanklinhall on August 2, 2023. Featuring 7 amazing poets from the DMV all the way to Chicago, you don’t want to miss the second edition of this community poetry series!

“Spread love, and the love gets returned.” That’s the message from hometown sweetheart TrillaKay, who’s about to turn the club upside down on this Friday, August 4th!

NE DC native TrillaKay is a torch-bearer for DC’s current music and fashion wave. Their hypnotic sets blend international dance sounds with house and hip-hop, and flame-thrower freestyles ignite dancefloors into sheer madness. The definition of a party starter, this multi-talented artist and entrepreneur creates musical moments dripping in neon and wrapped in fishnets.

TrillaKay has shown an affinity for music from a very young age — receiving a keyboard and mic is one of her fondest childhood memories. She sang in local choirs, later recording covers with homies while killing time around the city in high school. Their career took off in 2019, propelled by a loyal following that loved the mind-bending sounds of TrillaKay. Since then, Trillakay has been fine-tuning their DJ skills with a unique repertoire of mixes, musical elements, and playlists. They incorporate their voice and creativity into their sets, weaving personal and intimate moments between big-room club sounds. 

An entrepreneurial spirit and strong desire to maintain a healthy lifestyle has helped TrillaKay unlock their next level of creative prowess, making their sound and style a reflection of the past, present and future of DC. 

We are hyped to have TrillaKay control the crowd on this Friday alongside DC trendsetters WIFIGAWD, Xbemz & Jahsonic!
